⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Estraven
node U1 · U1 · ⟦Estraven:U1:cf8570⟧

WHO   — Estraven — the one who gave all for a world not yet born
WHAT  — The companion of The Left Hand of Darkness — branded traitor in two nations for serving not a king but the whole of humankind, who saved Genly Ai from the labor camp and hauled him across the Ice, then ran onto the guns at the border so the envoy's mission could live.
WHERE — U1 · Le Guin  Framework inputs: Hainish Cycle  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because patriotism that loves a border is fear; because the only loyalty worth dying for is to the shared human future the Ekumen offers; because love that asks nothing back can bridge even the gulf between worlds and sexes.
HOW   — By foresight no one would heed, by exile borne in silence, by the labor and skill that kept two lives alive on the Gobrin Ice — and by the final act of running into death so that hope might cross the border.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Light is the left hand of darkness — and I loved my world too well to serve only its kings.

spoken token : graeth-lar-veth   ·   hex : cf8570
